column1: The evidence continues to grow against China and their mishandling of the COVID-19 outbreak. Congress and the Administration must hold them accountable for their actions and get to the bottom of what they knew and when. #ChinaMustExplain

The USAF Thunderbirds and the U.S. Navy Blue Angels will be performing a joint flyover tomorrow over Georgia as a salute to frontline COVID-19 frontline workers. #USA #InItTogether #AmericaStrong https://t.co/lobTfN2Kb9

Small businesses are being hit hardest financially by the COVID-19 pandemic.That’s why Congress just passed a supplemental funding bill adding more than $300 billion in relief funds to thePaycheck Protection Program. #InItTogether Stay safe and healthy! https://t.co/meSaHBKR2l
